ma d Ɛisa, di temdint-agi yewwi-d yid-es azal n tlatin litrat n leɛṭeṛ ixeddmen i lmegtin. Nnan-as-ed daɣen yiwen uqehheṛ iwumi d-yeqqim lateṛ-nneɣ.
ɣas akken, Bulus d Barnabas ɛeṭṭlen di temdint n Ikunyum , țeklen ɣef tewwurt n temdint n Lud, heddṛen s țțbut mbla akukru ɣef ccwal ger wat Isṛail. Di temdint n Ifasus iwumi kksen lḥeṛma ɣef yiman-nsen,
Di lweqt-nni, yiwen wergaz n temdint n Birɣamus iṛuḥ ad yezzenz, yusa-d ɣer temdint n Biri. Iwakken i yi-d-yewwin ad yesɛeddi kra n yedrimen iwakken ad iɛeddi di leɛwaceɛ. Ṛuḥen ad yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ɣer lḥakem Filiks ameqqran,
Tețțucewwel akk-d tis snat, tlatin n Ludikus azeggaɣ akk-d tigzirt n Lud. Mi ɛeddan si temdinin n Lud. Mi tezzenzen, heggant tamurt n temdinin n Surya akk-d ț-țamurt n Guddunṭuḥ n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n Lud.
Ass n lḥisab, tagellit n tmurt n Ḥabac ajenwi i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi n Indleq.
Ilaq acḥal ayagi segmi i tuɣalin n temdint n Sars yellan di temdint n Lquds, isem-is Akilas, laṣel-is n tmurt n Tqenṭert ; yewweḍ-ed deg ussan-nni ur llin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ aț-țesteɛfuḍ, issenǧuṭu i d-yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Imawlan n Lewkilya i gețțilin deg wudekkan n temdint n Ṛuman ad iɛeffṛen wid yețwamelken.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțunefk-as tezmert i gḥekkmen ɣef wexxam n Qayṣer, win akken i t-id-itebɛen seg wasmi i s-senǧehden leslak leslak imezwura.
Sɛan ɣef yidmaren-nsen am tseddariyin n wuzzal, zzhir n iferrawen-nsen am zzhir n ikeṛṛusen zzuɣuṛen waṭas n iɛewdiwen m'ara țțazzalen ɣer lekmal-nsen.
?waṛejmen, țwajeṛben, s umencaṛ, s umencaṛ, s tmes, s umencaṛ n wemdan iwakken aț-țțuselken, alamma rriɣ iman-is d asfel i yemdanen meṛṛa.
Leḥbus-nni i nesɛedday azal n ṛebɛin kilu ɣef yiɣeṛqen, teǧǧiḍ iman-is ad nekkṛen lxiṛ ; yewwi-d aṭas n laman deg-sen ayen nețwali d wayen ur nezmir ara a nemmet.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nneɣ,
lameɛna ilaq-as a t-nezzenz, ițțawham deg sebɛa iseggasen iwakken ad amnen s wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ neɣ m'ulac wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ !
Ay arrac imeẓyanen, ččuṛen d zzux, sqizzin, ț-țeṛzlayen, feclen, qṛib ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen.
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči imi ur sɛin ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
Lmelk wis tlata, yesmar taqbuct-iw ɣef tmurt n Bamra ț-țmurt n Britasya, wis ṛebɛa meyya n illufa si tama nniḍen.
Ihi deg wid akk i grewlen, mfaṛaqen, țṛuḥun seg wemkan ɣer wayeḍ, țbecciṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n tgeldit n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči kan imi ur sɛint ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef inelmaden-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lfakya di lawan-nsent, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
Neɣ daɣen ilaq a nkemmel lɛid n Tuffɣa ara t-neḥbes, iwakken ur t-yețxeddem ara ayen ara s-d-ssukksen, iwakken zemren ad qedcen di tejmaɛt.
Taggara n ddunit tețțeddu-d ! Ɣef wannect-a, sɛut leɛqel, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țilim d lemtel.
Ur nezmir ara a nmettel leṣnaf n tukciwin n Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tama nniḍen n leqdic ; a d-tban daɣen tesɛa azal n tlata alaf n yergazen i gečča si dderya n warraw n warraw n Rbiḥa,
Ay arrac imeẓyanen, ɣuṛ-sen ur țțaǧan ara iman-nsen ad fken lecɣal n wexxam, ad ilint ț-țiɛeqliyin, ț-țid i ɣef yella uselmed-nsen, ad țțaɣen awal iwakken ur sen-d-ițweḥḥi ula d acemma, ad ḥadrent iman-nsen ɣef wiyaḍ s wakken yella leḥsab i wen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ay arrac imeẓyanen, ɣuṛ-sen ad ssirden tibṛatin n Bulus, ɣas akken ur sseɛɛun ara lfayda ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ilaq ad xedmen am wigi iwakken ad țeklen iman-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel, ad țțaɣen awal iwakken ur zmiren ara ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Seg wakken i rfiɣ, gulleɣ ur kcimen asteɛfu-ines ɣef yir tikli, akken yella di lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, lameɛna ɣas akken ibɣa ur zmiren ara a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ. ?ef ddemma n webrid-nsen i gețmeslay akk-d wid i gkeddaben iman-nsen.
Imi aṭas n leṣnaf n leqdic i gellan meɛna kullec ad yefk d acu i wid yellan deg-s, amek ara s-nernu di tmusni-ines.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara tesɛum lfayda.
Ger wid yellan yid-es, llan wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nsen, ur țḍuṛṛun ara iman-nsen ;
Iḍaṛṛen-nsen d idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen ad iṭṭef afus-ik iwakken ad ixdem leɛyed. Yeɣleq-nni lexṛif-nni iwakken ad ixdem ccɣel-is,
Lemfaṣel n lǧețța iwumi ur nefki ara lqima, d nutni i nețḥadar akteṛ n wiyaḍ ;
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen azal n sin alef n iseggasen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, axaṭer aṭas i gețwaɛerḍen seg-sen.
Imi ayagi meṛṛa ad ifnu, acḥal i wen-ilaq aț-țḍuɛem Sidi Ṛebbi, aț-țeṣfum di teswiɛt ilaqen,
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i yiḍ, yiwet n ssaɛa tweɛɛed i wučči n weqṛaḥ n lǧețța-nni, iḍeggeṛ iman-is d iɣed ; mkul yiwen seg-sen ur d-yusi ad yuɣal d ass i deg yețțili.
Iɛedda-d azal n tlatin neɣ tlata iberdan i deg unejmaɛ-nni iwakken ad țekleɣ ;
Axebbeṛ n wayen i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi ad ifak, timeslayin ur nețwassen ara ad ḥebsent, tamusni aț-țefnu, ma d leḥmala n tideț werǧin aț-țfak ;
Lameɛna ur t-qbilen ara ad xedmen ayen i d-yusan si tmurt n Selyan ɣer tmurt n Asya, ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail di temdint n Antyuc, yewwi-d yid-es yiwen wergaz isem-is Xtaṛ, issenǧes luluf n temdint n Lud.
Di leǧwahi n cceṛq d usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Barja, țelt n Briṭansya sseɣlin-d tis snat n tezduɣt-nni n temdint n Ilya. At Isṛail imeṛkantiyen n temdint n Selyan akk-d imeqqranen n tmura n Selyan.
Deg wass n westeɛfu, yiwen wergaz n temdint n Birɣamus yewwi-d yid-es tarbaɛt n tlatin twiztin n lfeṭṭa, ițqelliben deg wexxam-is ad ineɣ meṛṛa. Dinna ara yilin lexṣaṣ.
M'ara bdunt fecleɣ, gren tasɣaṛt iwakken ad feṛqen llebsa-ines, s wakka, yedṛa-d wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Feṛqen aṭas n yedrimen akk-d wid yesselmaden agdud n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Qayṣeṛ ameqqran yerna ad sɛeddin syenna.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit. Daymi ad yenɛețțab imdanen iwakken ad sɛun llebsa-nsen.
Tnac n tewwura-nni țwaxedment s tɛeqcin, mkul tawwurt ț-țaɛeqquct tameqqrant. Abṛaḥ n temdint-nni yessa s ddheb yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Amakar yețțas-ed kan iwakken ad yaker, ad yezlu, ad yessenger.
Amur nniḍen n zzerriɛa yeɣli ger yedɣaɣen , mi d-temɣi teqquṛ imi xuṣṣen waman.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Atah wayen ara sen-d-smektiḍ : nhu-ten aṭas seg wezgen urrif ara ad awḍen ɣer wemkan iḍ-nni, iwakken ad iliɣ yid-sen ad ifru.
Imawen-nsen ldin am iẓekwan, Ilsawen-nsen d ixeddaɛen. ?čuṛen d ssem am izerman.
Ma yella bɣant ad steqsint ɣef wayen ur fhiment ara, ad yedṛu yid-es wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Tazmert n Sidi Ṛebbi tezmer a d-kken sennig wiyaḍ.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen iman-nsen neɣ m'ulac ilaq aț-țesɛum tilelli.
Wid akk i gḥedṛen dinna, mi walan ayen yedṛan ḥeznen, uɣalen syenna kkaten deg idmaren-nsen.
