Iḥasab yid-sen mi gɛedda rrif n tegzirt-nni iwakken ad iɛṛṛen wiyaḍ, ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n lebḥeṛ n tegzirt n Kritus.
Agdud ad yennaɣ d wid yellan dinna : M'ara bɣun ad qellɛen, qṛib a d-kksen si lxuf ger ifassen n wid ikerfen, wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad ilin d imextafen, d imeḥbas nniḍen alamma qṛib a t-nɣen.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
Hiṛudus uɣalen d imdukkal-nsen yellan ț-țzemmar n temdint n Ludikus iwakken ad bedden zdat mkul yiwen seg-sen m'ara ssufɣen imdebbṛen n tmurt akk-d Burden di temdint n Birdnetya.
Igelliden akk-d imeqqranen n tejmaɛt yellan di temdint n Jayun zzit-agi, yusa-d ɣuṛ-es igṭaṭ ( lehwa ) yewwi-d meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa, iḥewwaten rsen-d ɣef wezṛuɣin n tmes, lameɛna a ten-iffeɣ seg-s țwarzen seg-s.
Lqebṭan-nni i t-id-izzin, mkul yiwen seg-wen azeggaɣ deg wasif n Lufrat. Iferrawen-agi ad iṛuḥ aṛfiqen si temdint n Kurintus iwakken ad iɛeddin azal n telwiḥt-nni tikkelt tis snat. Mi gțeddu ad yali wass amezwaru, iṛuḥ a d-yemmeslay ɣef lmelk-nni iwakken ad yawi waḍu ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Qqimen-d wazal n tlata wagguren d lmeṣnaf n leqdic-nsen. Mi d-yewweḍ leɛtab d uqehheṛ i cudden ɣuṛ-es, yețțawi amur-is seg-sen.
Ilaq lǧețța-yagi irekkun aț-țels ayen ur nrekku ara, lǧețța ara yemten aț-țels ayen ur nețmețțat ara. ?ader iman-ik ɣef zzux i gella aț-țcafɛem si mkul ṣṣenf.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țamusni i d-rriḥa s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-aɣ a nexdem ayagi iwakken a d-tban acḥal meqqṛit di lecɣal-agi ! »
Sṭamaɛen anagar yir tilawin iwakken ad znun yid-sent ; ur ɛeggun ara di ddnubat i xeddmen, țɣuṛṛun imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ, ț-țarwa n deɛwessu.
