Ɛiwzet ihi, țekleɣ ɣef yiman-nwen ayen yedṛan deg wexxam, iwakken aț-țissinem amek ara terrem awal ixedmen cceṛ.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Kra deg-sen i gxuṣṣen di liman deg wexxam-nsen, s wakka ma yella wiyaḍ țṛaǧun anagar ayen i d-yeqqimen seg-s.
Yiwen wergaz yeẓẓa tafeṛṛant di ddunit. Ihi ḥerzet tigedrin, aṭas deg i gemmuten deg wexxam-nwen.
S wakka, yedṛa-d wayen yuran di ddunit meṛṛa : tesseɛdeḍ aṭas n iberdan iwakken ad țemfaṛaqen wway gar-asen, daymi i s-d-yerra lexbaṛ n lxiṛat n Lmasiḥ i yiman-is.
