M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin : ur xellɛet ara, tețțeddum deg webrid n lefsad d zzhu, tɛebdem lemqamat, ulawen nwen ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ, ayen ara telsem d wayen ur nezmir a t-iṛuḥ ula d acemma.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Tijmaɛin n iberdan, sɛeddan ccetwa di ɛecṛa n temdinin-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ, d igellil neɣ d mkul ṣṣenf.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, d nutni i glaqen a ten-id-yaweḍ di lexṣaṣ, iwakken ad sɛun ayen ara ḥwiǧen.
Acḥal mennaɣ ad iɛeddi di tiṭ n tissegnit wala i unejmaɛ-nni iwakken ad țwaḥebseɣ.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, neɣ ɣef ddemma n tmusni-ines.
Ma yella tețqellibem ɣef ddunit-agi deg ujeṛṛeb ur t-tkeččem ara, aț-țuɣalem aț-țeṭṭfem deg webrid n ddunit-agi neɣ ɣef wid yeddren.
Ma d kunwi tḥeqṛem igellil ! Tqudṛem sin wussan i deg xeddmen, ama di teswiɛt-nni ama di lweqt i deg ilaq a d- fiḥelelelel iwakken ad iɛaqeb Sidi Ṛebbi.
Wid yesɛan imɛellmen i gețțamnen s Lmasiḥ ilaq ad kksen fell-asen leqdeṛ, ad qqimen deg-s wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen timeslayin ur nețwassen ara.
