Ad iɛaqeb widak-nni i gxeddmen lefsad, ițnadin anagar lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, imi ur țțaken ara lqima i lhiba n Sidi Ṛebbi. Ur țqadaṛen ara, qebbḥen, ur uggaden ara ad regmen ula d lmalayekkat.
D acuɣeṛ i s-d-yekkan seg wayen yellan di temdint n Lquds ?ṭuqqutet n temdint-agi ? Aṭas seg-sent tid ikerrzen akk-d azal n ṛebɛin kilu ;
Ațan tɛezrit aț-țerrem tagecrirt n lqaɛa, ț-țamezduɣt s lebḥuṛ armi d aman iẓuran i d-ikkan seg wezṛu.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ.
Akken daɣen ula d usenduq-nni igellil neɣ tijmaɛ n tmes i d-yezgan n usenduq, wwḍen-d meyya n 1600 si tezdayin n usenduq n temdint n Skurdud.
Aman-agi n leḥyuḍ-nneɣ am tseddariyin zzhir n ikeṛṛusen, zeddiget yerna leɛcuṛent-eț ț-țilawin izerman. Anaɣ ilaq a neččuṛen ula d nutni s ddheb yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen,
Akken daɣen i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Kritus iwakken ad iɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
Taggara n ddunit tețțeddu-d ! Ɣef wannect-a, sɛut leɛqel, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țizmirem aț-țeẓẓallem.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Aɛeqqa-yagi d nețța i d amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat yellan, lameɛna ilaq a t-iḍeggeṛ ɣer lqaɛa ; taɛessast akk-d yiwen i d-yețbanen iwakken ad iḍeggeṛ a t-iḍeggeṛ. M'ara t-id-yaweḍ, a t-yezzenz ula d wiyaḍ.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Lmelk yektal daɣen leɛli n leswaṛ n temdint s uɣanim-nni, yufa daɣen dinna qṛib a s-ceɛlen times deg-s.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen azal n meyya iberdan.
Imiren imdanen ad bdun ad ffɣen, ad rnun m'ara rren ɣer tmes, ad bɣun ad cwiṭ n lexyal.
Senket-aɣ-d si gar-aneɣ, d acu n tikciwin i sen-yexdafa Ṛebbi, yellan d Bab n tezmert ; ccetwa deg-sen meṛṛa si lɛinseṛ n ccṛeɛ akk-d imukan imezwura, s wakka ț-țideț ilaq a ten-nefɛen ;
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ;
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Țțuceggɛeɣ-d ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; ɣef ddemma-s i lliɣ d ameḥbus ; dɛut ihi iwakken a t-beccṛeɣ akken ilaq, mbla tugdi.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni.
A sen-tiniḍ annect-agi iwakken a d-tessakiḍ deg waṭas n lecɣal-nsen, ad sɛun ayen ara ḥwiǧen, yerna ad yehwan ɣef idrimen nniḍen.
Ma yella tesṭerḥbem yis s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, ɛasset iman-nwen, axaṭer mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka kan i gella.
Ur nezmir ara a d-nini : aț-țxelṣem tabzert i lḥukuma, anagar tajmaɛt n wid yellan si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen yellan di tmurt n Tyatir ur nețwassen ara. Deg umkan-agi n temdint n Kuriṭa ț-țmurt n Ikunyum d yergazen ara yilin di tmurt n iyunaniyen meṛṛa, ixemmimen-iw akk-d uselmed-agi meṛṛa.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ițeddun s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad iṛuḥ ɣuṛ-wen. Mmugreɣ-ed acḥal n tikkal i wid i kkun-ițweṣṣin s ɣuṛ-wen.
Axaṭer mkul tabṛaț i deg ara tebdam s wayen n diri i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi : ț-țagi i d-tekka yerna tǧehdem tideț di teswiɛt n tudert.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen di tegzirt n Kritus ț-țmeslayt n Kritus si tmurt n ddunit. Meɛna win akken i gɣilen izmer a d-yerr wid yellan di tgelda n Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țestenfeɛ.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Yiwen wass deg ussan-nni, yiwen si tejmaɛt n watmaten ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail wten-ten, laṣel-nsen di Tawṛat n Tawṛat s ɣuṛ-es, ț-țagi i d-tekka iwakken a sen-d-yețțunefken d lemtel.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d sebba n tuccḍa, agummaḍ i leḥjab yellan di tmurt-ik ilaq ad ițțujeṛṛeb ; s wakka aț-țfeṛḥem ayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, aț-țețțuɛerrim sennig n tmurt-ik.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ur neqbil ara ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura deg uqiḍun n temlilit ad rren lxiṛ s ddheb ɣef txeddem ?
Ma ulac win ara d-yesfehmen, neɣ m'ulac ad ssusmen axiṛ, ad yefk tazmert s wayes ara tecɛel tmes deg wayen ara s-d-rren.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, neɣ m'ulac ilaq-asen ad yaker tikciwin i d-ițasen ɣuṛ-wen.
Di yal taswiɛt, slet-ed mliḥ i mkul amkan anda ara ɛiwnen seg wayen yelhan, iwakken aț-țernim di yal amkan anda ara yilin tejmaɛt n watmaten n tmurt ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țagi i d tețxebbiṛeḍ s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi. »
Ɣef wayen yeɛnan ajmaɛ n yedrimen i temdinin ț-țudum, bɣan a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, a nexdem akken ilaq ; am akken daɣen ara t-sɛeddiḍ di lɛaddat-nsen.
Ma iwala ur s-izmir ara, ad fnun yid-sen ayen akken i t-id-nnan. Ur nezmir ara a nessusem si lehduṛ-agi.
Ma yella txeddmem lxilaf wway gar-awen, eɛni mačči d lbaṭel i d itekken seg ulamma n temdint anda i glaq aț-țɛiwnum, neɣ m'ulac qeblet-eț ?
iwakken a d-ḥeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-ek ayen akk i tegneḍ, a t-ineɛlen ; mačči d imeslayen-nwen i d-yekka meɛna d awal n Lmasiḥ i kkun-ițeffɣen seg-wen.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, qqen tiṭ-ik teldiḍ-ț, m'ara d-inṭeq leḥjab yellan di lexla.
M'ara d-yas yiwen di tegniț n lextaf-nni, qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer tuyat n lbabuṛ, iwakken ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt-nni, ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt-nni, iwakken ad jemɛen, ad țṛaǧun.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, ur tezmirem ara aț-țeččem a d-țfehmem lḥala n tmurt n Asya, kunwi daɣen ilaq a d-teṭṭfem di leqdic n watmaten n tmurt n Yahuda d wamek ara d-yuɣal lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ, a d-yawi kra n yemdanen seg-wen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
Am akken i t-id-ixebbeṛ Sidi Ṛebbi di mkul amkan di mkul amkan n tmurt, a wen-d-yefk tazmert s wayes ara theggim iman-nwen seg wayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen akk-d ṭṭabla ;
Ilaq acḥal ayagi segmi i tuɣalem d iselmaden, kunwi atan mazal teḥwaǧem win ara wen-islemden lumuṛ imezwura n wawal n Ṛebbi ; ur tezmirem ara i weɣṛum, mazal-ikkun teḥwaǧem ayefki.
?adret ɣef yiman-nwen ; atan win i kkun-ițweṣṣin, aț-țețțusellkem, ula d yiwen deg-wen aț-țeččem di lewṣaṣ, seg umenɣi i deg imecṭuḥen-agi yellan di lexṣaṣ, a ț-țideț ;
Ma yella tețḍeggiɛem leṛẓaq n ddunit-agi, ma yella tețțessem si tmura-agi, aț-țeččem di tegniț, ilaq daɣen aț-țxedmem akteṛ n wiyaḍ, aț-țeṭṭfem iman-nwen.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yețnerni di ddunit mkul amkan akk-d țmezduɣt n ddheb,
Di tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen, kra n wussan di temẓin, akk-d tmura n Akaya. Di tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen, kra n watmaten yellan di tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, ḥemmlen-t yerna ad a d-iniɣ, wid i d-yusan seg imukan imezwura di mkul amkan ;
Neɣ m'ulac wid yellan seddaw unejmaɛ-nni, ur nelli ara s ɣuṛ-ek m'ara d-yas wass-nni, neɣ m'ulac ad yekker ccwal ger wat Isṛail. M'ara ḥekmen fell-ak aț-țesɛuḍ leqdeṛ akteṛ n wiyaḍ,
Bɣiɣ aț-țeẓrem ayen akk i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, a wen-tessawḍem ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken ad rebḥen cciɛa ur nețdum ara ;
iwakken a kkun-qadṛen medden ɣef ddemma n tikli nwen yeṣfan, yerna m'ara tseddqem mbla lfayda.
Imi teẓram d acu n nnfeɛ-nwen, bɣiɣ aț-țɛeggdem, aț-țettixṛem i neyya d ṣṣfa n wul-nwen.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed n wemdan. S wakka ițbeggin-ed belli d ayen n diri i wiyaḍ ayen ara ḥwiǧen, nutni d lemtel-agi i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ-es :
ayen tesɛam d zzyada ad yenfeɛ wid ixuṣṣen meṛṛa iwakken asm'ara txuṣṣem kunwi, a ten-ɛiwnen s wayen sɛan d zzyada ; s wakka ihi aṭas n imukan-agi ɣer zdat inebgawen-is, ma d kra deg-sen yeznuzun itbiren.
Lameɛna amdebbeṛ di tejmaɛt ur ilaq ara ad afen deg-s lɣaci wayen ara s-d-ssukksen, kra wayen ara yedṛun yid-es wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ilaq a sen-t-id-yawi wayen ara sen-ssukksen, iwakken zemren ad qedcen di tejmaɛt.
Tețțubarek lebḥeṛ-nni i d-yusan aberkan aberkan ; aberkan aberkan adlis-nni mačči ɣef rrif n lebḥeṛ n Beltas akk-d leswaṛ n temdint n Lud. Tuɣal ț-țamezduɣt n temdint n Lud.
Nezger lebḥeṛ n wayen i d-yewḍen ɣer lmeqṣud-nni, amek ara iṛuḥ a d-yawi lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n Selyan.
Yerna mazal-ikkun tețzuxxum ! Ilaq-awen aț-țilim di leḥzen, argaz i gxeddmen annect-agi ilaq a t tessufɣem si gar-awen ; imdanen meṛṛa ttabaɛen ayagi yerna bɣan a kkun-ɛiwnen di tugniț, iwakken aț-țǧehdem.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut mliḥ deg yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țxelṣem tabzert i lḥukuma, iɣellien ɣer ṭṭabla iwakken aț-țeččem aț-țesseblem kra n wid i d-iskiddiben.
Sɛut iles aẓidan, imeslayen yesɛan lfayda, iwakken aț-țețțarram awal i yal yiwen s ṣṣwab.
Lameɛna ilaq ad kemmleɣ tikli-ines iwakken aț-țilim d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ ; ma yella wamek ara yilin di liman-nwen i dayem.
Imi teẓram d acu n nnfeɛ-nwen, bɣiɣ aț-țnernim di tikli-nwen ! Ilaq aț-țeẓrem daɣen belli acḥal n tikkal i gexṣeb ț-țagi i d-țmegraw, aț-țweṣṣim iman-nwen axaṭer aṭas imettel iman-nwen ɣer wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer temdint n Arimati akk-d Tyatirtir, tezzenzem ɣef tigejdit yellan ț-țigzirt n Afrika, wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ, ddukklent deg waṭas n tudrin n tmurt n Asya.
Si temdint n Kurintus, ccetki ɣef twaɣit tameqqrant n temdint n Yiriku, ɛeddan azal n tlatin litrat n Frijya qbel iwakken ad amnen s wayen yeɛnan tagelda n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma yella tesṭerḥbem yis-wen, feṛḥet imi tedduklem di temdint n Ifasus, acu n lfayda i kkun-id-yewwin ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ yellan deg webrid n Lmasiḥ ?
Ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger watmaten, ur ssimɣuṛet ara iman-nwen meɛna ddut s ujelkkaḍ ( s ucelliṭ ) yellan di tmurt n Yahuda.
Ma yella tețqellibem a n-ṛeǧmen si ddunit-agi, ɛiwzet iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen am weṛfiqen-nni di tmes, ad iṛuḥ ɣuṛ-wen ad iṛuḥ ɣer yiwet n tikkelt kan, ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi kra n wussan ɣer webrid n leslak.
Yiwen ur yezmir ad inkeṛ ayen i d-nnant tira iqedsen. Ma yella ccariɛa-nwen tsemma «iṛebbiten» akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa, ur tezmir ara aț-țesbedd lḥekma di lebḥeṛ, neɣ m'ulac aț-țeɣli lqima n leɛqed i deg-s.
D nețța i d-isbeggnen ccbiha n tideț akk-d tmanegt tameqqrant n Sidi Ṛebbi akken tella, s tezmert n wawal-is i gbedd lsas n ddunit meṛṛa. Mi gessazdeg imdanen si tmurt-nsen, yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma deg igenwan ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi ;
Ɣef wannect-agi, ur yebɣi ara a nali ɣer tama nniḍen n lebḥeṛ, ma yella bɣiɣ ad zegren timura i wuḍar n lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n Asya.
Mi d-tewweḍ tmeddit, Bulus yezṛu di temdint n Barja, ma d nukni yeǧǧa-yaɣ-d lewṣaya, win akken iwumi qqaṛen ccariɛa n Musa ;
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ : yewɛeṛ ɣer temdint n Jafa ț-țanezduɣt ajdid, ma d nețțat tedṛaḍa-agi ur s lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ ara.
Asm'akken i gennejmaɛ wegdud deg unezṛuf, ur ilaq ara ad yili d sebba s wayes ara wten deg-sen ger yemdanen n ddunit.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer lmeṣbeḥ n tmurt n Yahuda yellan d leǧwahi n tmura i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer lebḥuṛ i gbeddlen, isem-is Beninstad, d ameqqran di tejmaɛt n Lud.
Imezdaɣ n tmurt uggaden, dɣa iweḥḥa-yas-ed Sidi Ṛebbi, tamecṭuḥt i deg yella tezmert n Lǧameɛ iqedsen ; yis daɣen i d-ițwaxleq ddunit.
si tmurt n Trufim n Tyatir, i gellan di xemsa yitransist, llan gar-asen xemsa yitranyen n tezmar n Kurintus, Ikunyum d Antyuc yellan di tmurt n Tyatir, si tmurt n Selyan akk-d Tqenṭert.
Uriɣ-ed tabṛaț-agi imi țekleɣ ɣef lewkil n tgelda n igenwan.
Ṛebɛa iseggasen a d-yeǧǧa Sidi Ṛebbi di tlemmast n tejmaɛt, bɣan a d-awin ṛṛusul-nsen zdat iḍaṛṛen neɣ a ten-beḥten di lexṣaṣ.
Yiwen seg-sen i ḥesben d lexṛif i wemkan-nni, iqeṛṛeb-ed tikciwin ur yezmir ara ad iqleɛ iman-ik syagi tṛuḥeḍ ɣer wemkan iqedsen, m'ur yezmir ara a ten-yezzenzen, m'ara d-yezziren ur zmiren ara ad yawi yid-sen.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tmurt n Frijya akk-d Silisya, isseǧhad tijmaɛin n watmaten ur netqeddem ara ɣef tmurt n Frij. Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer tegzirt n Qubṛus,
Di mkul amkan nesla yedṛa leḥṛam d ameqqran gar-asen, d ayen ur nețțaf ara ulamma ger leǧnas nniḍen, tessawḍem armi yiwen deg-sen yețɛic di leḥṛam akk ț-țisirt, lameɛna aṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara.
Ma d kunwi akk-d wid meṛṛa yellan si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, țxebbiṛent s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi akken ilaq, rnan-d daɣen wid yesselmaden iman-nsen, rnan-d daɣen wid yesɛan tazmert ad xedmen yis-sen, ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq.
Aṭas n wat ddunit i gțeddun ț-țmeslayeḍ-ed fell-asen. ?ef ddemma-s daɣen i gella talwit i t-id-yewwin ț-țameqqrant.
?ef wayagi, ilaq-aɣ a nẓer belli di tmurt n Maṣeṛ, win akken i ten-issufɣen si tmurt n Maṣer, ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail axaṭer a s-nawi talwiḥt n tejmaɛt n watmaten yellan di lexṣaṣ, ț-țilawin-nsen di lexṣaṣ,
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Sɛut iles aẓidan, imeslayen yesɛan lfayda, iwakken aț-țețțarram awal i yal yiwen s ṣṣwab. ț-țikellax gar-asen i ț-țiqeddacin n tejmaɛt i llant yemdanen yid-sent, wid ur neǧhid ara di liman,
Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer Ṛebbi nețța i gḥekkmen ɣef yemdanen s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, wid ur nețwassen ara.
Deg wass-nni, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n ?ur d Sidun.
Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i ṭṭmeɛ n yedrimen akk-d wayen sɛan d zzyada .
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit ; ilaq ad yili d win iḥekkmen deg iman-is, d aɛeqli, d win iteddun s ṣṣwab.
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt lmegtin, ma yella wamek, aț-țeṭṭfem deg u?ekka.
Ula d kunwi daɣen ma teṭṭfem deg yiwet n tegmatin yeččuṛen d lfeṛḥ imi tedduklem akk-d tewwurt, tețṛuḥum ɣer tewwurt iwakken a wen-t-id-yefk.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tiseḍwa-nni s weɣyul, s wakken tella tezmert-nsen i geɣli.
Imawlan n leṣnaf n leqdic i gellan ɣer yemdanen meṛṛa, meɛna aṭas deg-sen i gemmuten ;
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen.
Ațan tɛezrit aț-țerfed tadist, a d-tesɛu aqcic ad ițțusemmi Iman ț-țagi i d-ițeffɣen seg wezṛu-ines.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent ur ugeffur, ur yețɣimi ara ad ixdem di lqaɛa, ad yini : țqaṛit i d-țeffɣen seg-s tbuciḍant-nni isem s wayes ara tedṛu d uquṛan.
